                <h4>Administrator Classroom Observation Tool (A-COT)</h4>

            </span>
            <p>In addition to the comprehensive Classroom Observation Tool, CLI Engage provides the Administrator-COT (A-COT), an abbreviated version of the tool that helps administrators focus their observations on instructional practices in preschool classrooms that are linked to important child outcomes.</p>
        </li>
    </ul>
    <ul>
